    <a title="Asghar Abbas" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/37421322-asghar-abbas"><img alt="Asghar Abbas" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1444319622p2/37421322.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1415788344?book_show_action=true">Oct 13, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Asghar Abbas" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Asghar Abbas" href="/user/show/37421322-asghar-abbas">Asghar Abbas</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9786055903183" href="/book/show/15703816-trainspotting">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1415788344" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17556229453624409344"><br/>Best Scottish thing ever. If you can read, as in just read this, then you are my hero. It&apos;s written in pure Scottish dialect. <br/><br/>And it&apos;s movie gave us a young Obi-Wan Kenobi. </span>
  <span id="freeText17556229453624409344" style="display:none"><br />Best Scottish thing ever. If you can read, as in just read this, then you are my hero. It's written in pure Scottish dialect. <br /><br />And it's movie gave us a young Obi-Wan Kenobi. </span>
